name: Copper and Silver Half Moon Earrings
description:
Hand wrought from 22g Copper sheet that has been hand cut, textured and soldered to a 16g Sterling  Silver wire.  Approx. 3/4 inches from top of ear wire to bottom of earring and 1/2 inches wide.
Beautiful, light weight, with great movement. Sterling Silver Ear wires.

name: Sterling Silver Geometric Arrowhead Earrings
description:
Hand wrought from 22g Sterling Silver sheet that has been hand cut, textured and soldered to an 18g Sterling  Silver wire that forms the top triangle.  Approx. 1.5 inches from top of ear wire to bottom of earring and .75 inches wide.
Beautiful, light weight, with great movement. Sterling Silver Ear wires.

name: Pineapple Quartz 3 Row Woven Cuff Bracelet
description: Warm, rich, yummy caramel colored Czech glass seed beads are sewn on brown leather cord. 4mm pineapple quartz natural stone beads glow with sunny charm. Hand made stamped copper button  is 1/2 inch in diameter. Bracelet measures 7", fits wrist 6-6 3/4" with a warm comfortable hug.

name: Stacked Copper and Turquoise Triple Bangle Set
description: This unique bangle set is made up of three hand forged copper bangles. Two bangle are hand forged and twisted and the third is hand forged with a turquoise cabochon set in Sterling Silver bezel. Size is a 2 1/2 inch inside diameter.

name: Metalic South Sea Pearl 5 Row Woven Cuff Bracelet
description: Want an accessory that you can wear with anything and everything? This chic 5 row woven cuff bracelet is it! 6mm south sea pearls in varying shades of silver, pewter and taupe are sewn on ivory leather cord. These beauties are surrounded with iridized Czech glass seed beads and then finished with a row of black onyx natural stone beads, classy and fun. 1 1/4 inch pewter flower button adds just the right touch of whimsy. Bracelet measures 7 1/4" fitting wrists 6-7". Go every where and do everything!

name: Turquoise and Copper 5 Row Woven Beaded Cuff Bracelet
description: One inch hand stamped and forged copper button is the "heart" of this woven cuff bracelet with a western flair. 4mm painted glass turquoise beads in the center, are sewn on brown leather cord. One row of multi colored Czech glass seed beads are finished off with another row of twinkling turquoise Czech glass seed beads. Bracelet measures 7 inches, will fit size 6-6 3/4" loose to snug. You must heart this beauty!

name: Brass Hoop Earrings Classic with a twist
description:
Hand Wrought Brass Hoop Earrings are approx. 2 inch wide. Made from Red Brass which looks more golden in Hue than standard Brass. 
Hand formed Sterling Silver ear wires. Strong and light weight they are a classic with a twist. The earrings have been hand polished with Renaissance Wax to deter tarnish.

name: Mixed Metal Bangle Set  (3)
description:
Bangle set of 3 mixed metals, Copper, Brass and Nickle silver. Hand Forged and riveted closed. This mixed metal look can go with just about any combination of colors, very versatile, and comfortable to wear they will quickly become a FAV. 
Size 7 1/2. 
2 1/2 inside diameter

name: Carnealian Red and Gold Beaded Cuff Bracelet
description: Warm 6 mm carnelian stone beads are the heart of this elegant wrap bracelet. Deep red carnelian 6 mm stones are set off by the gold czech glass seed beads. The look is rich, indulgent and classy. 1" handmade etched brass button, bracelet is 7 1/2" inches long, 1 1/4" wide, fits wrist size 6.5 - 7.25. Deep moroccan red leather cord is the perfect accent.

name: Earth Colored Beaded Wrap Bracelet
description: Five complimentary colors of Czech glass seed beads are sewn on brown Greek leather to create a earthy Moroccan flavored wrap bracelet. Iridescent bronze, pearl, tortoise shell, gold and burnt orange Czech glass seed beads end with a whimsical elephant button. It's made for you! Measures 34 inches long with adjustable loop closeted will wrap 5 times around a 7-8 inch wrist.

name: Wide Copper Convex Bangle Synclastic Bracelet
description:
Classic Copper Cuff Bracelet Convex/Rounded shape 1.25" wide. Arizona Copper has been cut and formed on a sinusoidal stake. The surface is lightly textured with a rounded hammer. Light but not too light weight 20 gauge pure Copper.The bracelet has been left its natural color and treated with "Renaissance Wax" to deter tarnishing. The openings are well rounded making it comfortable to wear. Make a statement with this bracelet. M 7-71/2
*Hand Wrought in Arizona

name: Elephant Love, Peace and Wisdom Earrings
description: Brass hand cut Elephant silhouettes dangle from sterling silver ear wires. Riveted silver eyes give these little guys a great personality. Each elephant is approximately 1 1/8" from top of ear wire and 3/4 " across. Graced with 6mm  Green Aventurine stones and stamped with a Lotus flower.  There are 2 finishes, with the flower stamped plus the bead or without the bead or stamping (third picture).

name: Vesica Pisces Drop Golden Brass Earrings
description: Brass earrings are hand cut, stamped and polished. Sterling silver handmade ear wires allow even the most sensitive ears a comfortable experience. These really pick up and reflect light, you will be noticed! 2.5 inch long from top ear wire x 1 inch wide

name: Elephant Love, Peace and Wisdom Pendant Necklace
description:
Elephant Love, Peace and Wisdom Pendant is hand cut, forged and riveted. Meant to be a "grounding" influence for the wearer.   Hand Forging has aged the metal for a vintage look. The Pendant measures 1 3/8 " X 1 1/4" Brass Chain included. 
Made to order.

name: Black and White Dalmation Jasper Wrap Bracelet
description: "Dalmatian" Jasper beads (8mm) strung on 1 mm leather cord and secured with a handmade silver button. Adjustable between 6-7.

name: Copper Braided Cuff
description:
Cuff is hand formed with 8 gauge copper wire. It's been set in a rolling mill and the ends soldered. Size is 7-7 1/2. 
The lustrous beauty of Copper is well displayed in this piece. Wear it stacked or alone.

name: Copper Fold Form Cuff Bracelet
description: Hand cut and Formed 20 Gauge Copper Cuff. Size 7-7 1/2

name: White Crystals and Pearls Bracelet
description: Fresh as a daisy, delicate, pure, and very feminine. This three row white woven bracelet is made with white pearl Czech glass seed beads surrounding 6mm cut Czech crystal rounds, sewn on white pearlized leather cord.  Antiqued pewter button clasp easily closes this wrap bracelet, measures 7".

name: Earthly Pleasures Copper Toned Bracelet
description:
Earth tones and golden hues glisten from this handmade  
woven cuff bracelet. One of a kind hand stamped and forged 1 inch Arizona Copper button is the star here! Perfectly stunning Czech glass crystals in pale amber, bronze and peach tones, surrounded with tortoise shell Czech glass seed beads make this your new favorite bracelet. Measures 6 and 3/4 inches, fits wrists 6- 6 1/2. Fall colors you can wear year round!

name: Brass hoop earrings
description: Hand Wrought Brass Hoop Earrings are approx. 2.25 inch wide. Made from Red Brass ( new gold ) which looks more golden in Hue than standard Brass. Hand formed Sterling Silver ear wires. Strong and light weight they are a classic. The earrings have been hand polished with Renaissance Wax to deter tarnish.

name: Brass and Copper Cuff Bracelet
description: Unusual twisted wire cuff. Hand crafted from 6 gauge and 10 gauge wire. Twisted and soldered. Size 6 1/2 to 7 approx.

name: Peach and Pale Blue Natural Stone Beaded Cuff Wrap Bracelet
description: Red Aventurine 6 mm natural stone beads are really peach or apricot in color. Layered between pale blue Czech glass seed beads, yellow jasper 4 mm natural stone completes this five row beaded cuff wrap bracelet. One and one quarter inches wide, this bracelet makes a big statement. 7/8" metal button with tropical leaf motif gives an organic style. Both classy and relaxed this bracelet goes from day to evening wear effortlessly.

name: Elephant Love, Peace and Wisdom Bracelet
description:
Adorable pewter elephant button begins this sparkly pink and black wrap bracelet. Pretty pale pink Czech glass seed bead wind around and around your wrist bringing you love peace and wisdom, plus many many compliments! Hand sewn on black leather cord, adjustable loops at the end for flexibility.
Pink symbolizes: Love, Beauty, Kindness, Compassion
Pink is the color of universal love and compassion. Bracelet measures 42 inches to first loop, 2nd loop is 43 inches, wraps 7 times around wrist size 6-6 1/2 or 6 times around larger wrists.

name: Brass Cuff with circle design
description:
Brass anti-clastic Cuff.  Hand cut, forged and stamped with a circle design. The piece has also been patina-ted to give an aged appearance.   
Size fits a 6.5 to 7 inch wrist.

name: Chunky Solid Copper Cuff
description:
Size 6 1/2 - 7 Chunky Solid Copper. Simple Hammered design has been tumbled and polished to a natural Copper sheen. Very comfortable and simple to care for. Keep it polished or let it patina on its own.
Great Energy Conductor.
Instructions on care will be included with your purchase.

name: Black and Gold Triple Wrap Bracelet
description: Looking for some boho chic? You found it! This sparkly little triple wrap bracelet is made with 3.2 mm faceted brass beads. Rich black 1 mm leather cord lays around the wrist perfectly. Handmade hammered brass button allows easy closure. Bracelet is 19" long or made to order. Fabulous alone or great for layering.

name: Tibetan Bowl Ring
description: A trilogy of metals, brass, copper and silver mix together in this simple but stunning Tibetan bowl ring. Size 61/2 with 1/4" brass shank, the bowl consists of 1" textured copper disk, with smaller brass and silver disks riveted together. Modern but timeless, this ring will bring you peace for years to come.

name: Pretty In Pink Sparkling Goddess Beaded Cuff
description: Sweet simple pink seed beads surround 6mm sparkling Czech glass crystals on this beaded cuff style bracelet. Beads are sewn on black leather. 3/4" pewter goddess button makes this bracelet extra feminine and unique. Measures 7.5 inches, fits size 7-7.5 inch wrists.

name: Double  Hoop Brass Earrings
description: The brass hoops are linked one with the other, the smaller hoop is a rounded square linked to the larger circle hoop. Hand wrought with Sterling Silver ear wires.

name: Silver Beads on Mint Leather Cord. Chan Lu style 5 Wrap Bracelet
description: Wonderful mint and silver combination is perfect for summer and into fall. Chan Lu style five row wrap bracelet features 4 mm nickel plated brass beads sewn on mint leather cord. Handmade nickel silver button is hammered and polished to a bright luster. Bracelet is 34 inches long, and will fit size 7-8 wrists with its adjustable closure. Simple and elegant, great with any apparel!

name: Braided Brass Cuff
description:
Brass cuff is made from 2 strands of 10 gauge and one of 12 gauge wire that has been braided, set in a rolling mill and soldered. The cuff is perfect for stacking or wearing alone. 
Size is 6 1/2 to 7

name: Pink Quartz and  Czech Glass  Woven Beaded Cuff Bracelet
description: Lovely pink 6mm quartz natural stone beads are stunningly mixed with silver centered pink czech glass seed beads. Add another layer of 4 mm pale pink quartz and you have an amazing five row woven cuff bracelet. One mm burgundy leather cord and 1" Italian silver button make this the perfect choice for pink lovers everywhere! Bracelet is a generous 1" wide and fits wrists 7"-7.5".

name: Purple Amethyst Beaded Wrap Cuff Bracelet with Multicolored Seed Beads
description: Purple Amethyst 6 mm natural stone beads are edged in Czech glass seed beads in shades of purple, blue, green, gold and silver. The outer row is 4mm Amethyst natural stone. Sewn on brown leather cord, this bracelet features an etched brass button with a leaf pattern. Button measures 1", bracelet is 1" wide and will fit wrist size 7.5" to 8".

name: Sea Green Aventurine and Amethyst Woven Wrap Bracelet
description: Beautiful sea green 6 mm Aventurine beads are surrounded by a wild mix of Czech glass seed beads in greens and iridescent purples. 4 mm Amethyst beads with a true deep purple hue make this a must have 5 row wrap bracelet. 7/8" silver tone pewter steam punk button anchors all these beautiful stones around your wrist. Bracelet is 1 and 1/4" wide and fits wrist size 6.5' to 7".

name: Hammered Brass Sea Turtle Earrings
description: Adorable sea turtles for your ears! 6mm aventurine stones hang from sterling silver hand shaped ear wires, featuring 1" hammered hand cut brass sea turtles with silver rivet eyes.

name: Five Wrap Bracelet Brass Beads on Coral Leather
description: Simple and elegant Chan Lu style five wrap bracelet features 4 mm brass beads sewn on coral leather. Button is 1/2 inch hammered hand made brass. Adjustable closure, to fit wrists 7-8 inches, bracelet measures 34 inches at last loop. Sophisticated, feminine and smart!

name: Copper Ruffle Fold Formed Earrings
description: Unique copper fold formed earrings have a very organic feel. Hand forged tumbled for strength and shine. Measuring approx. 2 inched from top of ear wire to the tip. A coating of preservation wax has been applied . These earrings are made to order so slight variations may occur. Beautiful movement and shine.

name: Woven Cuff Bracelet with Gold and Silver South Sea Pearls
description: Amazing metallic colored south sea 8 mm pearls are the center of this 5 row cuff. Surrounded with Czech glass pearl seed beads and metallic seed beads, the pearls really glow! Beautiful 1 inch pewter button closure. Measures 7.25 inches long and 1.25 inches wide. Classy and elegant, ready to show off year round!

name: American Indian Style Multicolored Beaded Cuff
description: A vivid mix of Czech glass seed beads surround vintage orange white heart trading beads in this decidedly American Indian Style beaded cuff bracelet. Hand made etched copper button 1". Bracelet measures 7 1/4" to fit wrist size 6-7". Perfect accent piece for that white shirt and jeans outfit.

name: Gauged Hoop Earrings, Brass
description: Brass hoop earrings. Hand forged from 14 gauge solid brass. The diameter of the hoop is 2 1/2 inches. Light weight, natural Brass color. Polished with Renaissance Wax to resist tarnishing. Everyday Classic self closing hoops. For Gauged ears.

name: Brass Handmade Cuff bracelet AntiClastic / Concave Golden
description:
Brass Cuff Bracelet is made from 20 gauge Brass that was formed on a sinusoidal stake. Its stylishness and comfortable wear make this piece a go to for most any occasion.
Made from Red Brass which has more of a golden color than that of standard Yellow Brass. one inch wide Size 6.5 to 7 inches  
*Hand Wrought in Arizona

name: Multicolored Beaded Wrap Bracelet
description: My personal favorite! 4 feet of hand sewn Czech glass multicolored seed beads wrap 7 times around a 7-71/2" wrist. Adorable pewter elephant button brings whimsy and of course luck! May be ordered to fit your wrist size, multicolored seed beads will vary. Sewn on very thin 1mm brown Greek leather, this bracelet will go every where, every day!

name: Silver Hoops With Silver Beads Chandelier Earrings
description: Chandelier Earrings of Nickel silver and silver plated beads in this unique design. Sterling silver ear wires also handmade. Size is Approx. 1.5 inches wide and 2.5 inches long from ear wire tip.These are so light you won't know you are wearing them until the compliments start coming!

name: Chan Lu Style Silver and Black Triple Wrap Bracelet
description: Looking for some boho chic? You found it! This sparkly little wrap is made with 3.2 mm nickel silver beads sewn on rich buttery soft black leather. Handmade nickel silver hammered button makes for easy closure. Measures 19" long or request length. Fabulous alone or worn in layers.

name: Black and Pearl Beaded Cuff Bracelet
description: This beaded cuff features 6 mm Dalmation Jasper stones in the center row and is surrounded by Czech glass seed beads in pearl and black.The button is handmade by us in nickel silver it is etched with a floral motif. This bracelet can be dressed up or down, great with jeans or an elegant black dress. Please specify size when ordering. Measures 1" wide, 7/8" button. Really stunning!

name: Wide Brass Cuff Synclastic Convex Golden Hue
description: Hand Wrought from 20 gauge Brass. Measures approx. 1.5 inches wide, a classic statement piece. The cuff was hand formed on a sinusoidal stake, the surface was then lightly textured with a rounded hammer. Size 7.5 - 8. Very comfortable to wear. Make a statement with this bracelet.

name: Brass Fold Form Cuff Bracelet
description:
The Brass Cuff is adjustable between 7-71/2. Beautifully Formed to give a comfortable fit.  Made from 20 Gauge Red Brass. Red Brass gives a more golden hue than the standard yellow Brass.
Made to order.

name: Copper Crescent, Fold Form Earrings
description: Copper earrings are formed from sheet Copper. Hand forged into an inverted Crescent shape. The natural Copper color has been polished with Renaissance Wax to resist tarnishing. Approx. 7/8 inch to 1 inch in diameter. Handmade Sterling Silver Ear Wires. Very light weight with a wonderful Copper sheen.
